<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-3"><a href="Pidyon_haben#Exemptions"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Exemptions</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="Pidyon_haben#Ceremony"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Ceremony</span></a></li>
