</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-7"><a href="Pidyon_haben#Women_and_Pidyon_HaBen"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Women and Pidyon HaBen</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-8"><a href="Pidyon_haben#Traditional_Jewish_interpretation"><span class="tocnumber">6</span> <span class="toctext">Traditional Jewish interpretation</span></a></li>
